fields.title: Zigzag
fields.description:
Hand loomed by local artisans with 100% Natural Cotton

Can be used as sauna towel, beach towel, bath towel, gym and yoga towel, scarf, sarong, tablecloth, picnic blanket, light throw and much more.

Light and airy
Quick drying
Extremely absorbent
Eco-Friendly
Soft
Large in size and yet compact
Convenient for travel
Authentic and versatile
Thin
Softer and more absorbent with every wash
 

Machine wash max 40C, do not use fabric softener

It may reduce the towel’s ability to absorb water
